<title>USA: Fuisz Technologies names McVey as new CEO.</title>
<headline>Fuisz Technologies names McVey as new CEO.</headline>
<dateline>CHANTILLY, Va. 1997-04-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>Fuisz Technologies Ltd said Friday that its board of directors had appointed Kenneth McVey to succeed Dr. Richard Fuisz as president and chief executive officer.</p>
<p>McVey is the chief executive of the company's Fuisz International Holdings Ltd subsidiary, based in Dublin, and will remain in that post, the company said. In addition, Fuisz will continue in his original role as chairman of the board, it said.</p>
<p>Fuisz Technologies develops and commercializes drug delivery and food applications.</p>
